## Development

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/Romamo/py-invoices
cd py-invoices

# Install with dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Type checking
mypy py_invoices

# Linting
ruff check py_invoices
```

